data.description: 3 bedroom Port Orange. No HOA! Seller motivated! Bring all offers.  Move in ready home. This home features new carpet and has been freshly painted. Large open kitchen with lots of cabinets. French doors leading out to the enclosed Florida room which overlooks the fenced in backyard. A/C only 2.5 years old.Conveniently located just minutes from the beach, highways, shopping, and restaurants! All information recorded in the MLS is intended to be accurate but cannot be guaranteed.
